General.Name: Hamama
General.Description: Hamama Meir Trading (1996) Ltd. imports and distributes raw materials for the food industry in Israel. It offers grains, pulses, nuts, dried fruits, seeds and herbs, coffee, and animal feed. The company serves food conglomerates, wholesalers and distributors, small and medium-sized natural food stores, and health food shops. Hamama Meir Trading (1996) Ltd. was founded in 1996 and is headquartered in Bnei Brak, Israel.
